itemDisplayName: Deploy a 10 node, 2 node type Windows Service Fabric Cluster
description: This template allows you to deploy 10 Node, 2 node type Service Fabric Cluster with one node type exclusively supporting Stateless workloads on  Standard_D2_V2 Size VMSS.
summary: This template takes a minimum amount of parameters and deploys a 10 Node, 2 node type, Stateless Windows Service Fabric Cluster
